<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Maintenance Request Updated - PropertyOS</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #3b82f6;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #3b82f6;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 0;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #1f2937;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #4f46e5;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .info-value {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .status {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background-color: #dbeafe;
      color: #1e40af;
    }
    .update-box {
      background-color: #eff6ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .update-box h4 {
      color: #1e40af;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #4338ca;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>PropertyOS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Maintenance Request Updated</h2>
      <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p>There is an update on your maintenance request.</p>

      {{#if updateMessage}}
      <div class="update-box">
        <h4>ðŸ“‹ Update:</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0;">{{updateMessage}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Request Title</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{requestTitle}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Current Status</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="status">{{status}}</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Property</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{propertyAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Unit</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{unitNumber}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Request ID</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{requestId}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if trackingUrl}}
      <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">View Full Details</a>
      {{/if}}

      <p>If you have any questions about this update or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} PropertyOS. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>